    <title type="html"><![CDATA[讓Octopress有中文分類及側邊列]]></title>
    <link href="http://selfecy.com/blog/2013/07/13/rang-octopressyou-zhong-wen-fen-lei-ji-ce-bian-lie/"/>
    <updated>2013-07-13T00:18:00+08:00</updated>
